::Suka::

"What the hell?!" Suka yells out as the the ships pass and leave behind
50 cents. Several troops surround the two coins, all guns aimed at them
just in case.

"I want someone to go get those coins analized! I want to know anyone
who's ever so much as breathed on them! DNA scans, fuel leftovers, get
anything you can from them and analize it!" Suka barks out, using
his feet to push troops out of the way as he makes his way toward the
coins. "I don't want any surprises. Now!"

Several troops scoop up the coins, carrying them back to base for
analizing.
